      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIVERSDALE MICK (7) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh (25.46) in a Special conditions H at Shepparton. Has a good record here including five wins. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Better than last start and worth following up. HOLDEN BALE (4) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (30.51) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Should be in this for a long way. GO GO EVIE (1) hit the ground running from a squeeze draw and prominent early but run ended and faded to finish 6th at this track in Free For All company. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. The form from her last run stacks up well. Key player if finds best. WILD SERENA (8) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
